{"tid":1254383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣地鐵站支持警察攤位","createTime":"2019-06-24T05:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T10:08:12.000Z","uid":130722,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"39551a816e26f32019dda9aeafb427abc3ee6604","tid":1254383,"uid":130722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:54:20.000Z","msg":"住愉景新城方向<br />\n已經擺左好幾日<br />\n前幾日想拎一張掉但班仆街只係長期企係度扮派比人 唔派比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱今日路過拎左三張<br />\n大家路過記得支持下拎曬佢啲單張等佢唔使派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91daa1d8de636b3f91ddd664c918e3fc53ebaf7d","tid":1254383,"uid":94834,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"因為你唔係廢老"},{"pid":"0653c738e601c874860e9b5fe3420fce74ccb9c5","tid":1254383,"uid":130722,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"91daa1d8de636b3f91ddd664c918e3fc53ebaf7d","tid":1254383,"uid":94834,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"因為你唔係廢老"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:01:26.000Z","msg":"我見佢其實得好少單張咋<br />\n有啲中年大叔佢都唔派<br />\n<br />\n大家路過幫佢早啲收檔啦<br />\n雙面彩印<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59291f6152258f6d3993c79cd88a4223c03f92e","tid":1254383,"uid":130722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67ecc2ee4962a9a46fc935e9ac40f1ca3f0ace2","tid":1254383,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"站內定站外？"},{"pid":"8a2f5a19c5aabc57f5ac02c4692be6ce681413c9","tid":1254383,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱</span></strong><br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n個server會on99咁好慢 凌晨時份會好啲 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=0b46f498\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=c7873412\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=1b097ed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=c89fb4ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=6dcca06e\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=35033868\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=b8db994f\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"871fb4ad1fc409c5afb69cbbe093da8f19b2355d","tid":1254383,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"呢類攤檔係其他區見到既話麻煩都報一報，方便有巴絲路過下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90fe162e87303a04d8fad23e328c5d2912b35d9","tid":1254383,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"攞完 當面撕咗佢"},{"pid":"7e0330e04e9da3ada2270560f07720c1a635c865","tid":1254383,"uid":130722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a67ecc2ee4962a9a46fc935e9ac40f1ca3f0ace2","tid":1254383,"uid":2